This is how to solution of lst:
   Remember that total is 0
   Remember that n is lst's length
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      Remember that x is item i in lst
      When remainder of x and 2 is 1, then:
         Remember that total is sum of total and x
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is total
